16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 4005 of Title 56, unless there
19 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 A. For Medicaid managed care plans, the Oklahoma Health Care
21 Authority shall ensure that the insurers, health plans, and managed
22 care plans comply with federal and state laws, rules, and
23 regulations applicable to coverage for mental health or substance
24 use disorder services.
